name: 94 N - S Rd, Falmer, Brighton BN1 9QH, UK
directions:
Pevensey1 Level 2

From the East side entrance (under the bridge cafe) take the corridor directly ahead from the entrance. The corridor will open up to the right, gender neutral toilets can be found around the corner on the left. 

Taking the west side entrance (from the courtyard) take the first two flights of stairs up to level 1. Here you'll find the lecture theatres and an option of two opposite flights of stairs. Take the stairs facing East, so that the lecture theatres are on your left. Go through the doors in the corner to the right. Follow the narrow corridor around to the right and through two sets of doors until it opens up to a larger corridor - gender neutral toilets can be found to the right.
